Goal:

   Provide a web app to link together people who have ideas and people who doesn't.
   Most like Google Summer of Code than real job.

Way:

   - Have a web site
   - Search for existing ideas
   - Search for ideas already implemented
   - add an idea
   - set some capabilities and availabilities
   - Describe methods and share experience about join an existing project or create his own

Tech:

   - Node.js
   - MongoDB
   - Nginx
   - Want to play with full static site and REST APIs/Websockets
   - HTML5
   - Connected with source control sites
   - Load LinkedIn like profiles

First:

   - Have a site
   - Implement adding an idea
   - Don't forget unit tests
